{"word":"H8071 - שִׂמְלָה - simlâh - sim-law' - Apparel","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<strong>மூல வார்த்தை / Original: </strong><span class=\"hebrewOrGreek\">שִׂמְלָה</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>எழுத்துமாற்றம் / Transliteration: </strong>simlâh"},{"paragraph":"<strong>ஒலிபெயர்ப்பு / Phonetic: </strong>sim-law'"},{"paragraph":"<strong>சுருக்க விளக்கம் / Short Definition: </strong>Apparel"},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"வஸ்திரம், உடை, உடுப்பு, புடவை - பெண்பால் பெயர்ச்சொல்."},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"a wrapper, a mantle, a covering garment, garments, clothes, raiment, a cloth"},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"spacer\"></span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"parts-of-speech\"><strong>Part(s) of speech:</strong> Noun Feminine / பெயர்ச்சொல் (பெண்பால்)</span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"spacer\"></span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"original-in-english\"><strong>ஆங்கில மூலம் / Original in English:</strong> Perhaps by permutation for the feminine of <a href=\"#/H5566 - סֶמֶל - çemel - seh'-mel/5566\">H5566</a> (through the idea of a <i>cover</i> assuming the shape of the object beneath); a <i>dress</i>, especially a <i>mantle</i>: - apparel, cloth (-es, -ing), garment, raiment. Compare <a href=\"#/H8008 - שַׂלְמָה - salmâh - sal-maw'/8008\">H8008</a>."},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"spacer\"></span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Cognate:</strong> <a href=\"#/H8008 - שַׂלְמָה - salmâh - sal-maw'/8008\">H8008</a>, <a href=\"#/H8071 - שִׂמְלָה - simlâh - sim-law'/8071\">H8071</a>, <a href=\"#/H8072 - שַׂמְלָה - Samlâh - sam-law'/8072\">H8072</a>, <a href=\"#/H8079 - שְׂמָמִית - sᵉmâmîyth - sem-aw-meeth'/8079\">H8079</a>"}]}